title: Stop F**king Worrying Already
itunes:title: Stop F**king Worrying Already
description:
A recent study found that 85% of what you are worrying about will NEVER happen, so why do you still do it?

In this episode, I am going to teach you how to get past your worry and what to replace your worry with!
